---
title: Plant-Based Chick'n & Potato Mash with Caramelised Onion Sauce & Steamed Veggies
description: We better set an extra place at the table tonight because nostalgia is coming over and it’s bringing this veggie version
of homey chicken and potato mash. Cook up a caramelised onion sauce to put a spin on this classic.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/650bd161eed20ab36dc717b6-b1deda5e.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/650bd161eed20ab36dc717b6.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
